The paper deals with the task of generating natural language descriptions for animated GIFs or video clips, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The dataset and benchmark introduced in the paper can also be useful for multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) tasks. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques for the task, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
